tplinkBandWidthMIB.name: tplinkBandWidthMIB

revisions.description: Initial version of this MIB module.

tplinkBandWidthMIB.description: Private MIB for system time configuration.

tpRateLimitTable.name: tpRateLimitTable
tpRateLimitTable.description: A list of rate limit entries. Here you can configure the traffic rate on each port.

tpRateLimitEntry.name: tpRateLimitEntry
tpRateLimitEntry.description: An entry contains of the information of rate limit.

tpRateLimitPort.name: tpRateLimitPort
tpRateLimitPort.description: The port number of the Switch.

tpRateLimitIngressRate.name: tpRateLimitIngressRate
tpRateLimitIngressRate.description: Set the bandwidth for receiving packets on the port.

tpRateLimitEgressRate.name: tpRateLimitEgressRate
tpRateLimitEgressRate.description: Set the bandwidth for sending packets on the port.

tpRateLimitPortLag.name: tpRateLimitPortLag
tpRateLimitPortLag.description: The LAG number which the port belongs to.

tpStormControlEnPPSTable.name: tpStormControlEnPPSTable
tpStormControlEnPPSTable.description: A list of storm control entries. Here you can configure the port PPS mode with PPS enabled or disabled. Configure this table before the storm control mode and rate configuring.

tpStormControlModeTable.name: tpStormControlModeTable
tpStormControlModeTable.description: A list of storm control entries. Here you can configure the port storm control mode with kbps, ratio or pps. Configure this table before the storm control rate configuring.

tpStormControlTable.name: tpStormControlTable
tpStormControlTable.description: A list of storm control entries. Here you can configure the bandwidth for forwarding packets.

tpStormControlEnPPSEntry.name: tpStormControlEnPPSEntry
tpStormControlEnPPSEntry.description: An entry contains of the information of storm control PPS mode.

tpStormControlEnPPSPort.name: tpStormControlEnPPSPort
tpStormControlEnPPSPort.description: The port number of the Switch.

tpStormControlEnablePPS.name: tpStormControlEnablePPS
tpStormControlEnablePPS.description: The storm control rate mode configuration: Disable: kbps & ratio mode is avalible with this status. Enable: enable PPS mode, only pps mode is avalible.

tpStormControlEnPPSPortLag.name: tpStormControlEnPPSPortLag
tpStormControlEnPPSPortLag.description: The LAG number which the port belongs to.

tpStormControlModeEntry.name: tpStormControlModeEntry
tpStormControlModeEntry.description: An entry contains of the information of storm control rate mode.

tpStormControlModePort.name: tpStormControlModePort
tpStormControlModePort.description: The port number of the Switch.

tpStormControlBroadCastRateMode.name: tpStormControlBroadCastRateMode
tpStormControlBroadCastRateMode.description: Broadcast rate mode configuration. Configure kbps & ratio with the 'tpStormControlEnablePPS' setting to disable. Configure pps with the 'tpStormControlEnablePPS' setting to enable.

tpStormControlMultiCastRateMode.name: tpStormControlMultiCastRateMode
tpStormControlMultiCastRateMode.description: Multicast rate mode configuration. Configure kbps & ratio with the 'tpStormControlEnablePPS' setting to disable. Configure pps with the 'tpStormControlEnablePPS' setting to enable.

tpStormControlULRateMode.name: tpStormControlULRateMode
tpStormControlULRateMode.description: UL-Frame rate mode configuration. Configure kbps & ratio with the 'tpStormControlEnablePPS' setting to disable. Configure pps with the 'tpStormControlEnablePPS' setting to enable.

tpStormControlModePortLag.name: tpStormControlModePortLag
tpStormControlModePortLag.description: The LAG number which the port belongs to.

tpStormControlEntry.name: tpStormControlEntry
tpStormControlEntry.description: An entry contains of the information of storm control.

tpStormControlPort.name: tpStormControlPort
tpStormControlPort.description: The port number of the Switch.

tpStormControlBroadCastRate.name: tpStormControlBroadCastRate
tpStormControlBroadCastRate.description: Set the bandwidth for receiving broadcast packets on the port. The packet traffic exceeding the bandwidth will be discarded. kbps(0-1000000) ratio(0-100) pps(0-1488000) Set it 0 to disable the storm control function for the port.

tpStormControlMultiCastRate.name: tpStormControlMultiCastRate
tpStormControlMultiCastRate.description: Set the bandwidth for receiving multicast packets on the port. The packet traffic exceeding the bandwidth will be discarded. kbps(0-1000000) ratio(0-100) pps(0-1488000) Set it 0 to disable the storm control function for the port.

tpStormControlULRate.name: tpStormControlULRate
tpStormControlULRate.description: Set the bandwidth for receiving UL-Frame on the port. The packet traffic exceeding the bandwidth will be discarded. kbps(0-1000000) ratio(0-100) pps(0-1488000) Set it 0 to disable the storm control function for the port.

tpStormControlPortLag.name: tpStormControlPortLag
tpStormControlPortLag.description: The LAG number which the port belongs to.

tpBroadcastRateExceed.name: tpBroadcastRateExceed
tpBroadcastRateExceed.description: An broadcastRateExceed notification is sent when the value of broadcast stormControl rate set of port is exceeded. Note that if you need this notification, the value of broadcast stormControl rate of port must be set. The transmission of stormControl notifications are throttled by the agent three sesonds every time.

tpMulticastRateExceed.name: tpMulticastRateExceed
tpMulticastRateExceed.description: An stormControl notification is sent when the value of multicast stormControl rate set of port is exceeded. Note that if you need this notification, the value of multicast stormControl rate of port must be set. The transmission of stormControl notifications are throttled by the agent three sesonds every time.

tpIngressRateExceed.name: tpIngressRateExceed
tpIngressRateExceed.description: An ingressRateExceed notification is sent when the value of ingress rate set of port is exceeded. Note that if you need this notification, the value of ingress rate of port must be set.The transmission of ingressRateExceed notifications are throttled by the agent three sesonds every time.

tpEgressRateExceed.name: tpEgressRateExceed
tpEgressRateExceed.description: An egressRateExceed notification is sent when the value of egress rate set of port is exceeded. Note that if you need this notification, the value of egress rate of port must be set.The transmission of egressRateExceed notifications are throttled by the agent three sesonds every time.
